// servicenow_incident (SCD2). There are NO *_display_value columns (OM-22) — all names/groups are
// derived. The "source view" referenced in older notes is the legacy SQL Server view, retained
// only as the authoritative business-rule reference (e.g. Req_Status_Grouped).
