//    Exclusion strings CONFIRMED: infoict (Informational) + normalot (Normal Change Request OT).
// B. [OM-12] dim_change_risk raw int -> name. NAME SET CONFIRMED from "Total by Risk": Low(710),
//    Moderate(157), Medium(55), High(27). Map each int to a name by matching the counts.
// C. [OM-9] dim_change_status: confirm raw close_code value set + casing (comparison is case-insensitive
//    as a safeguard). Individual state names (New/Assess/...) unconfirmed; group rule is authoritative.
// D. [OM-5] has_business_impact: chg.impact is categorical (1=High,2=Medium,3=Low). Decide boolean flag
//    vs business_impact_level varchar. Option (b) needs a modelling-gate re-review.
// E. [OM-8] change_type_description: no source field in the ingestion (confirmed blocked).
// F. [OM-11] dim_incident_priority full value set; is_high_priority = priority IN (1,2) CONFIRMED.
// G. [OM-14] primary date role for the Power BI active relationship (assumed opened_date_key).
// H. [OM-13] accumulating-snapshot windowed build for fact_change_request (AE).
